;W[qs]LB[rr:1][rq:2][qs:3]C[Dia.3 Correct / 2,2 point

The 2,2 point is the vital point in this problem.  If Black plays there he's alive so it's a case of "Your opponent's vital point is your vital point."  This means that even though Black looked big in the beginning, he had insufficient eyespace to live.
